
sumadhvavijayaH madhvavijayaH

prathamaH sargaH

kAntAya kalyANaguNaikadhAmne navadyunAthapratimaprabhAya
nArAyaNAyAkhilakAraNAya shrIprANanAthAya namaskarOmi || 1-1 ||

anAkulaM gOkulamullalAsa yatpAlitaM nityamanAvilAtmA
tasmai namO nIradanIlabhAse kRSNAya kRSNAramaNapriyAya || 1-2 ||

api trilOkyA bahirullasantI tamOharantI muhurAntaraM ca
dishyAddRshaM nO vishadAM jayantI madhvasya kIrtirdinanAthadIptim || 1-3 ||

tamOnudA.anandamavApa lOkastattvapradIpAkRtigOgaNena
yadAsya shItAMshu bhuvA gurUM stAM strivikramAryANpraNamAmi varyAN || 1-4 ||

mukundabhaktyai gurubhaktijAyai satAM prasattyai ca nirantarAyai
garIyasIM vishvagurOrvishuddhAM vakSyAmi vAyOravatAralIlAm || 1-5 ||

tAM mantravarNairanuvarNanIyAM sharvendrapUrvairapi vaktukAme
sa~NkSipnuvAkye mayi mandabuddhau santO guNADhyAH karuNAM kriyAsuH || 1-6 ||

uccAvacA yena samastaceSTAH kiM tatra citraM caritaM nivedyam
kintUttamashlOkashikhAmaNInAM manOvishuddhyai caritAnuvAdaH || 1-7 ||

mAlAkRtastaccaritAkhyaratnairasUkSmadRSTeH sakutUhalasya
pUrvAparIkAramathAparaM vA kSAmyantu me hanta muhurmahAntaH || 1-8 ||

shrIvallabhAjnAM sasurendrayA~ncAM sambhAvya sambhAvyatamAM trilOkyAm
prANeshvaraH prANigaNapraNetA guruH satAM kesariNO gRhe.abhUt || 1-9 ||

ye ye guNA nAma jagat prasiddhA yaM teSu teSu sma nidarshayanti
sAkSAnmahAbhAgavataprabarhaM shrImantamenaM hanumantamAhuH || 1-10 ||

karmANi kurvaNparamAdbhutAni sabhAsu daivISu sabhAjitAni
sugrIvamitraM sa jagat pavitraM ramApatiM rAmatanuM dadarsha || 1-11 ||

pAdAravindapraNatO harIndrastadA mahAbhaktibharAbhinunnaH
agrAhi padmOdarasundarAbhyAM dOrbhyAM purANena sa pUruSeNa || 1-12 ||

adAryasAlAvalidAraNena vyApAditendraprabhavena tena
prAdyOtaniprItikRtA nikAmaM madhudviSA sandidishe sa vIraH || 1-13 ||

karNAntamAnIya guNagrahItrA rAmeNa muktO raNa kOvidena
sphurannasau vairibhaya~NkarO.abhUtsatpakSapAtI pradarO yathA.agryaH || 1-14 ||

gObhiH samAnanditarUpasItaH svavahninirdagdhapalAshirAshiH
ahO hanUmannavavAridO.asau tIrNAmbudhirviSNupade nanAma || 1-15 ||

apakSapAtI puruSastrilOkyAmabhOgabhOktA patagAdhirAjam
vishvambharaM bibhradasau jigAya tvarAparAkrAntiSu citrametat || 1-16 ||

nibaddhya setuM raghuvaM shaketu bhrUbha~NgasambhrAntapayOdhimadhye
muSTiprahAraM dashakAya sItA santarjanAgryOttarameSakO.adAt || 1-17 ||

jAjvalyamAnOjjvalarAghavAgnau cakre sa sugrIvasuyAyajUke
AdhvaryavaM yuddhamakhe pratiprasthAtrA sumitrAtanayena sAkam || 1-18 ||

rAmArcane yO nayataH prasUnaM dvAbhyAM karAbhyAmabhavatprayatnaH
ekena dOSNA nayatO girIndraM sa~njIvanAdyAshrayamasya nAbhUt || 1-19 ||

sa dAritAriM paramaM pumAM saM samanvayAsInnaradevaputryA
vahnipraveshAdhigatAtmashuddhyA virAjitaM kA~ncanamAlayeva || 1-20 ||

shyAmaM smitAsyaM pRthudIrghahastaM sarOjanetraM gajarAjayAtram
vapurjaganma~Ngal. ameSa dRgbhyAM cirAdayOdhyAdhipateH siSeve || 1-21 ||

rAjyAbhiSeke.avasite.atra sItA preSThAya nastAM bhajatAM disheti
rAmasya vANyA maNima~njumAlAvyAjena dIrghAM karuNAM babandha || 1-22 ||

hRdOrusauhArdabhRtA.adhimaulinyastena hastena dayArdradRSTyA
sevAprasannO.amRtakalpavAcA didesha devaH sahabhOgamasmai || 1-23 ||

preSThO na rAmasya babhUva tasmANna rAmarAjye.asulabhaM ca ki~ncit
tatpAdasevAratireSa naicchat tathApi bhOgAnnanu sA viraktiH || 1-24 ||

namO namO nAtha namO namaste namO namO rAma namO namaste
punaHpunaste caraNAravindaM namAmi nAtheti namaNsa reme || 1-25 ||

kiM varNayAmaH paramaM prasAdaM sItApatestatra hariprabarhe
mu~ncanmahIM nityaniSevaNArthaM svAtmAnamevaiSa dadau yadasmai || 1-26 ||

svAnandahetau bhajatAM janAnAM magnaH sadA rAmakathAsudhAyAm
asAvidAnIM ca niSevamANO rAmaM patiM kimpuruSe kilAste || 1-27 ||

tasyaiva vAyOravatAramenaM santO dvitIyaM pravadanti bhImam
spRSTyaiva yaM prItimatA.anilena narendrakAntA suSuve.atra kuntI || 1-28 ||

indrAyudhaM hIndrakarAbhinunnaM ciccheda pakSANkSitidhAriNAM prAk
bibheda bhUbhRdvapura~Ngasa~NgAccitraM sa pannO jananIkarAgrAt || 1-29 ||

pure kumAranalasAnvihArANnirIkSya sarvAnapi mandalIlaH
kaishOralIlAM hatasiM hasa~NghAM vane pravRttAM smarati sma sUtkaH || 1-30 ||

bhuktaM ca jIrNaM paripanthidattaM viSaM viSaNNO viSabhRdgaNO.ataH
pramANakOTeH sa hi helayA.agAnnedaM jagajjIvanade.atra citram || 1-31 ||

dagdhvA puraM yOgabalAt sa niryandharmAniva svANsahajANdadhAnaH
adAribhAvena jagat supUjyO yOgIva nArAyaNamAsasAda || 1-32 ||

samarpya kRtyAni kRtI kRtAni vyAsAya bhUmne sukRtAni tAvat
kariSyamANAni ca tasya pUjAM sa~NkalpayAmAsa sa shuddhabuddhiH || 1-33 ||

viSNOH padashridbakasaM nirAsI kSiptAnyapakSiprakaraH supakSaH
sasOdarO.athAdita rAjahaM saH sa rAjahaM sImiva rAjakanyAm || 1-34 ||

indIvarashrIjayasundarAbhaM smerAnanenduM dayitaM mukundam
svamAtuleyaM kamalAyatAkSaM samabhyanandatsucirAya bhImaH || 1-35 ||

mahAgadaM caNDaraNaM pRthivyAM bArhadrathaM ma~NkSu nirasya vIraH
rAjAnamatyujjvalarAjasUyaM cakAra gOvindasurendrajAbhyAm || 1-36 ||

duHshAsanenAkulitANpriyAyAH sUkSmAnarAlAnasitAM shca keshAn
jighAM sayA vairijanasya tIkSNaH sa kRSNasarpAniva sa~ncikAya || 1-37 ||

jAjvalyamAnasya vane vane.alaM didhakSataH pArthivasArthamugram
sattvAni puM sAM bhayadAni nAshaM vRkOdarAgnergurutejasA.apuH || 1-38 ||

bhOgAdhikAbhOgavatO.aruNAkSAnitastataH sa~ncalatO dharendre
bahUndvijihvANmaNimatpurOgANasau kaTUNkrOdhavashANjaghAna || 1-39 ||

athaiSa veSAntara bhasmalInaH krameNa vAyuprabhavaH sutejAH
ruddhAkhilAshaM mukharaM pracaNDaM bhasmIcakArAkhilakIcakaugham || 1-40 ||

sa kRSNavartmA vijayena yuktO muhurmahAhetidharO.apradhRSyaH
bhISmadvijAdyairatibhISaNAbhaM vipakSakakSaM kSapayaNvireje || 1-41 ||

tarasvinaH prOccalitAn adhIrAn nirdagdhapakSAn atitIkSNakOpAn
sa dhArtarASTrANbahuhetilIlO vinAshya vishvANparayA shriyA.abhAt || 1-42 ||

kRSNA~Nghripa~NkeruhabhR~NgarAjaH kRSNAmukhAmbhOruhahaM sarAjaH
prajAsarOjAvalirashmirAjaH sasOdarO.arAjata vIrarAjaH || 1-43 ||

pautre pavitrAhvayajAmipautre dharAM nidhAyAsuradhISu tApam
kIrtiM trilOkyAM hRdaye mukundaM bheje padaM svaM sahajaiH sa bhImaH || 1-44 ||

viSNOH padAntaM bhajatA.anilena ghOrapraghAtairiti nAshitAste
rasOjjhitAshca~ncalavRttayO.alaM shObhAM na bhejuH suravairimeghAH || 1-45 ||

etat pratIpaM kila kartukAmA naSTaujasaH sa~NkaTamevamApya
mukundavaiguNyakathAM svayOgyAM kAle kalAvAkalayanta te.alam || 1-46 ||

yO bhUrivairO maNimANmRtaH prAg vAgmI bubhUSuH paritOSiteshaH
sa sa~NkarAkhyO.a~NghritaleSu jajne spRdhA.apare.apyAsurihAsurendrAH || 1-47 ||

sAnnAyyamavyaktahRdAkhubhugvA shvA vA purODAshamasArakAmaH
maNisrajaM vA plavagO.avyavasthO jagrAha vedAdikameSa pApaH || 1-48 ||

janO namennAparatheti mattvA shaThashcaturthAshramameSa bheje
padmAkaraM vA kaluSaM cikIrSuH sudurdamO duSTagajO vishuddham || 1-49 ||

avaidikaM mAdhyamikaM nirastaM nirIkSya tatpakSasupakSapAtI
tameva pakSaM pratipAdukO.asau nyarUrupaNmArgamihAnurUpam || 1-50 ||

asatpade.asansadasadviviktaM mAyAkhyayA saM vRtimabhyadhatta
brahmApyakhaNDaM bata shUnyasiddhyai pracchannabauddhO.ayamataH prasiddhaH || 1-51 ||

yad brahmasUtrOtkarabhAskaraM ca prakAshayantaM sakalaM svagObhiH
acUcurad vedasamUhavAhaM tatO mahAtaskaramenamAhuH || 1-52 ||

svasUtrajAtasya viruddhabhASI tadbhASyakArO.ahamiti bruvaNyaH
taM tatkSaNAdyO na didhakSati sma sa vyAsarUpO bhagavANkSamAbdhiH || 1-53 ||

nigamasanmaNidIpagaNO.abhavat taduruvAggaNapa~NkanigUD habhAH
aviduSAmiti sa~NkaratAkaraH sa kila sa~Nkara ityabhishushruve || 1-54 ||

vishvaM mithyA vibhuraguNavANAtmanAM nAsti bhedO
daityA itthaM vyadadhata girAM dikSu bhUyaH prasiddhim
AnandAdyairguruguNagaNaiH pUritO vAsudevO
mandaM mandaM manasi ca satAM hanta nUnaM tirO.abhUt || 1-55 ||

iti shrImatkavikulatilaka trivikramapaNDitAcAryasuta
nArAyaNapaNDitAcAryaviracite shrImatsumadhvavijaye
mahAkAvye AnandA~Nke prathamaH sargaH


dvitIyaH sargaH

vijnAnabhAnumati kAlabalena lIne durbhASyasantamasasantatitO jane.andhe
mArgAt satAM skhalati khinnahRdO mukundaM devAshcaturmukhamukhAH sharaNaM prajagmuH || 2-1 ||

nAthaH kalau triyugahUtiranudbubhUSuH brahmANamapyanavatAramanAdidikSuH
sarvajnamanyamanavekSya sakAryavIryaM smerAnanO bhuvana jIvanamAbabhASe || 2-2 ||

vedAntamArgaparimArgaNadInadUnA daivIH prajA visharaNAH karuNApadaM naH
AnandayeH sumukha bhUSitabhUmibhAgO rUpAntareNa mama sadguNanirNayena || 2-3 ||

AdeshamaulimaNimujjvalavarNamenaM baddhA~njalirmarudanarghamadhattamUrdhnA
hArAvalImiva hRdA vibudhendrayA~ncAM bibhrannijAnanujighRkSuravAtitIrSat || 2-4 ||

kAlaH sa eva samavartata nAma yAvat cintAkulaM vividhasAdhukulaM babhUva
vedAntasantatakRtAntarasaM na vidmaH shreyO labhemahi kathaM nu vayaM bateti || 2-5 ||

tatprItaye rajatapIThapurAdhivAsI devO vivesha puruSaM shubhasUcanAya
prApte mahAya mahitAya mahAjanaughe kOlAhalena sukutUhalini pravRtte || 2-6 ||

AviSTavAnakushalaM puruSaM prakRtyA pratyAyayannijajanAnnitarAmanRtyat
uttu~Ngaketushikhare sa kRtA~NgahArO ra~NgAntare naTa ivAkhilavismayAtmA || 2-7 ||

AbhASya sO.atra janatAM shapathAnuviddhaM uccairidaM vacanamuddhRtadOrbabhASe
utpatsyate jagati vishvajanInavRttiH vishvajna eva bhagavAnacirAdiheti || 2-8 ||

sadvIpavArinidhisaptakabhUtadhAtryA madhye.api karmabhuvi bhAratanAmakhaNDe
kAle kalau suvimalAnvayalabdhajanmA sanmadhyagehakulamaulimaNirdvijO.abhUt || 2-9 ||

vedAdrisadrajatapIT hapureshvarAbhyAM grAmO vibhUSitataraH shivarUpyanAmA
hemAdrirAjavibhurAjadilAvRtAbha- stasyAbhavad guruguNaH khalu mUlabhUmiH || 2-10 ||

rAmAdhiveshitaharisvasRmaulimAlA- rAjadvimAnagirishObhitamadhyuvAsa
kSetraM sa pAjakapadaM trikulaikaketuH kaM yaddadhAti satataM khalu vishvapAjAt || 2-11 ||

arthaM kamapyanavamaM puruSArthahetuM puM sAM pradAtumucitAmucitasvarUpAm
kanyAM suvarNalasitAmiva vedavidyAM jagrAha vipravRSabhapratipAditAM saH || 2-12 ||

reme.acchayOpaniSadeva mahAvivekO bhaktyaiva shuddhakaraNaH paramashritA.alam
mithyAbhimAnarahitaH parayeva muktyA svAnandasantatikRtA sa tayA dvijendraH || 2-13 ||

tasya prabhOshcaraNayOH kuladevatAyA bhaktiM babandha nijadharmarataH sa dhIraH
vijnAtabhAratapurANamahArahasyaM yaM bhaTTa ityabhivadanti janA vinItam || 2-14 ||

gOvindasundarakathAsudhayA sa nRNAM Anandayanna kila kevalamindriyANi
kintu prabhO rajatapIThapure padAbjaM shrIvallabhasya bhajatAmapi daivatAnAm || 2-15 ||

itthaM harerguNakathAsudhayA sutRptO nairguNyavAdiSu janeSvapi sAgraheSu
tattve sa kAlacaladhIratisaM shayAluH dhImANdhiyA shravaNashOdhitayA pradadhyau || 2-16 ||

trAtA ya eva narakAtsa hi putranAmA mukhyAvanaM na sulabhaM puruSAdapUrNAt
tasmAtsamastavidapatyamavadyahInaM vidyAkarAkRti labhemahi kairupAyaiH || 2-17 ||

pUrve.api kardamaparAsharapANDumukhyA yatsevayA guNagaNADhyamapatyamApuH
taM pUrNasadguNatanuM karuNAmRtAbdhiM nArAyaNaM kulapatiM sharaNaM vrajema || 2-18 ||

itthaM vicintya sa vicintyamananyabandhuH preSThapradaM rajatapIThapurAdhivAsam
bhaktyA bhavAbdhibhayabha~NgadayA shubhAtmA bheje bhuja~NgashayanaM dviSaDabdakAlam || 2-19 ||

patnyA samaM bhagavataH sa bhajaNpadAbjaM bhOgANlaghUnapi punarlaghayA~ncakAra
dAntaM svayaM ca hRdayaM damayA~ncakAra svacchaM ca dehamadhikaM vimalIcakAra || 2-20 ||

tIvraiH payOvratamukhairvividhairvratAgryai- rjAyApatI guNagaNArNavaputrakAmau
sampUrNapUruSamatOSayatAM nitAntaM deveritAviva purA.aditikashyapau tau || 2-21 ||

nAthasya bhUrikaruNAsudhayA.abhiSiktau shrIshrIdharapratatisArasharIrayaSTI
bhUrivrataprabhavadivyasukAntimantau tau dehashuddhimatimAtramathAlabhetAm || 2-22 ||

kAntAdRtau samucite.atha babhAra garbhaM sA bhUsurendraduhitA jagatAM sukhAya
acchAmbareva rajanI paripUritAshA bhAvinyapAstatamasaM vidhumAdyapakSAt || 2-23 ||

taM pUrvapakSasitabimbamiva pravRddhaM yAvad dvijendravanitA suSuve.atra tAvat
aM shena vAyuravatIrya sa rUpyapIThe viSNuM praNamya bhavanaM prayayau tadIyam || 2-24 ||

sampUrNalakSaNacaNaM navarAjamAna- dvArAntaraM paramasundaramandiraM tat
rAjeva satpuravaraM bhuvanAdhirAjO niSkAsayaNparamasau bhagavAnvivesha || 2-25 ||

santuSyatAM sakalasannikarairasadbhiH khidyeta vAyurayamAvirabhUt pRthivyAm
AkhyannitIva suradundubhimandranAdaH prAshrAvi kautukavashairiha mAnavaishca || 2-26 ||

nAthaM niSevya bhavanAnatidUramAptaH prAjnO mahaprakRtadundubhinAdapUrvAt
putrOdbhavashravaNatO mahadApya saukhyaM jnAnaM parOkSapadamapyamateSTahetum || 2-27 ||

Avishya veshma nijanandanaminduvaktraM bhUyO.abhinandya sa mukundadayAM pravandya
jAtasya tasya guNajAtavahasya jAta karmAdikarmanivahaM vidadhe sukarmA || 2-28 ||

jnAnArthameva yadabhUdasudeva eSa yadvAsudeva padabhaktirataH sadA.asau
tadvAsudevapadamanvavadaNsurendrA- stAtena yannigaditaM sutanAmakartrA || 2-29 ||

pAtuM payAM si shishave kila gOpradO.asmai pUrvAlayaH svasutasUnutayA prajAtaH
nirvANahetumalabhISTa parAtmavidyAM dAnaM dhruvaM phalati pAtraguNAnukUlyAt || 2-30 ||

atrastameva satataM pariphullacakSuH kAntyA viDambitanavendu jagatyanarghyam
tatputraratnamupagRhya kadAcidAptaH svasvAmine budha upAyanamArpayatsaH || 2-31 ||

natvA hariM rajatapIThapurAdhivAsaM bAlasya sampadamanApadamarthayitvA
sAkaM sutena parivArajanAnvitO.asau prAyAnnishIthasamaye nijameva dhAma || 2-32 ||

dOSeyuSAM samamanena vane.atibhIme tatkrIDitagraha ihaikatamaM tutOda
udvAntaraktamavalOkya tamabhyadhAyi kenApyahO na shishutut kathameSa ittham || 2-33 ||

Avishya pUruSamuvAca mahAgrahO.asau asmadvihArasamayOpagatANsamastAn
yacchaktiguptirahitAnalamasmi hantuM lOkeshvaraH sa bata bAlatamaH kileti || 2-34 ||

stanyena bAlamanutOSya muhuH svadhAmnO mAtA kadAcana yayau virahAsahA.api
vishvasya vishvaparipAlakapAlanAya kanyAM nijAmanuguNAM kila bhIrureSA || 2-35 ||

sA bAlakaM praruditaM parisAntvayantI mugdhAkSareNa vacasA.anuninAya mugdhA
mA tAta tAta sumukheti punaH prarOdI- rmAtA tanOti rucitaM tvaritaM taveti || 2-36 ||

rOde kriyAsamabhihArata eva vRtte pOtasya mAtari cirAdapi nAgatAyAm
jagrAha bAlamatha caikSata mAtRmArgaM sA.api kriyAsamabhihArata eva bAlA || 2-37 ||

kartavyamauDhyamabhipadya nirUpya sA taM prAbhOjayat khalu kulitthakulaM prapakvam
shItaM payO.api satataM paripAyayantI yasyOSNarOgamativelamasha~NkatAmbA || 2-38 ||

nUnaM pipAsuratirOditi hanta bAlO dhi~N mAM dayAvirahitAM parakRtyasaktAm
ityAkulA gRhamupetya tadA prasannaM pUrNOdaraM sutamavaikSata viprapatnI || 2-39 ||

pRSTvA.avagamya sakalaM ca tataH pravRttaM yUnAM ca duHsahamidaM shishunOpabhuktam
itthaM vicintya tanayAM bahu bhartsayantyA bhItaM tayA.anu kupitaM manasA.anutaptam || 2-40 ||

ArOgyashAlini tadA.api pureva putre vismeratAmupajagAma jananyamuSya
yasya trilOkajananI jananI viSe.api pIte na vismayamavApa samastashakteH || 2-41 ||

stanyaM muhuH kila dadau jananI gRhItvA kSemAya taM kila dadhajjanakO jajApa
anyO janO.api kila lAlayati sma kintu sarvO.api tanmukhasuhAsarasAyanOtkaH || 2-42 ||

devAdisadbhiranupAlitayA.adareNa devyAtmaneva vilasatpadayA nitAntam
avyaktayA prathamatO vadane.asya vANyA shAlInayeva bhuvanArcitayA vijahre || 2-43 ||

prAgri~NkhaNaM svayamatha sthithimeSa cakre pashcAdgatiM paricayena kila krameNa
vishvasya ceSTitamahO yadanugraheNa sarvaM tadasya pavanasya viDambanaM hi || 2-44 ||

pucchAntamacchamavalambya kadAcideSa prAtarvrajAdvrajata eva nijarrSabhasya
prAyAt priyasya sahasA svajanairadRSTO nanAvaneSu caratashcaratastRNAni || 2-45 ||

uttu~NgashR~Ngalasitasya mahiSThamUrteH pAdAvRtAvanitalasya surandhrakasya
Ashritya tasya shushubhe.avayavaikadeshaM bAlO divAkara ivOdayaparvatasya || 2-46 ||

lIlAM karOti nu gRhAntaragO nu bAlaH kUpAntare nu patitaH prakRtisvatantraH
itthaM vicintya sa muhuH svajanO vimRgya hantAnavekSya tanayaM hRdi tApamApa || 2-47 ||

bAlasya bAlaparilambanagOcaraM ta- dvashvasyatApivacanaM vanagOcarOktam
yat sAyamaikSata janaH shishumAvrajantaM ekAbdakaM vRSabhabAlakRtAvalambam || 2-48 ||

cintAmaNIndramiva cintitadaM daridrO vijnAnamArgamiva viSNuparaM mumukSuH
naSTaM ca nandanamiti svajanO.asya labdhvA nAthasya tasya tamanugrahameva mene || 2-49 ||

lIlAvasAnasamaye sahasA kadAcid AryO.amunA.abhyavahRtiM prati cOdyamAnaH
rOddhaiSa nO.asti dhanikO vRSavikrayIti prOvAca nandanamukhendumavekSya mandam || 2-50 ||

lIlAkareNa sa kareNa sukOmalena bIjAntarANi kila kAnicidAshu tasmai
smitvA.arbhakO.abhimataniSkapade yadA.adA- dAdatta tAni dhanikO bahumAnapUrvam || 2-51 ||

labdhaM sutAditi vadaNdvijapu~Ngavena kAlAntare nijadhane pratiditsite.api
sAkSAdamAnavanavAkRtitaH sa lebhe bIjacchalena puruSArthamahO vishiSTam || 2-52 ||

vAsudevamiha vAsudevatAsatkalAmabhinananda taM janaH
vAsudevamiti vAsudevasannAmakaM vividhalIlamarbhakam || 2-53 ||

iti viharati mahyAM viSNudAse.api gUDhe samajani sujanAnAM cittamAnandapUrNam
udayati ghanamAlAlInabhAnau ca bhAnau nanu jananayanAbjairlabhyate.alaM vikAsaH || 2-54 ||

iti shrImatkavikulatilaka trivikramapaNDitAcAryasuta
nArAyaNapaNDitAcAryaviracite shrImatsumadhvavijaye
mahAkAvye AnandA~Nke dvitIyaH sargaH


tRtIyaH sargaH

atha kadAcana sundaranandanasmitamukhendudRshAM dayitau nRNAm
mahamitO nijabandhumude mudA prayayatuH svajanaiH saha dampatI || 3-1 ||

svajanatApagamAgamasa~NgamapratisabhAjitapUrvakasambhrame
aviduSI jananIti sa bAlakaH sharaNatO raNatO niragAnnRbhiH || 3-2 ||

kva nu yiyAsasi tAta na sAmprataM svajanasantyajanaM tava sAmpratam
iti vibhuH pathikairuditO vrajaNsmitamanAkulamuttaramAtanOt || 3-3 ||

tvaritametya sa kAnanadevatAsadanamatra nanAma ramApatim
api tataH pragatO laghunArikelyupapadAntarasadmagataM ca tam || 3-4 ||

nalinanAbhanibhAlanasanmadAgamavikasvarabhAsvaralOcanaH
janamanOnayanAmbujabhAskarO rajatapIThapuraM prayayAvasau || 3-5 ||

suhayamedhagaNAtishayAlavO harinamaskRtayaH sukRtA imAH
iti surairapi bhUsuramaNDalaiH samanamat sa savismayamIkSitaH || 3-6 ||

na hi hariM satataM na namatyasau na ca na pashyati nApi na vandate
api tatheti vidhAya visheSataH sa nanu sAdhujanANsamashikSayat || 3-7 ||

anavalOkya sutaM sutavatsalO mRgayati sma mahIsurapu~NgavaH
muhurapRcchadamuSya gatiM narANpathi pathi pragatO.anupadaM drutam || 3-8 ||

janasadAgatisUcitavartmanA pratipadaM vrajatA parayA tRSA
dvijamahAmadhupena manOharaM smitamalAbhi sutAnanavArijam || 3-9 ||

virahadUnatayOdgamanOnmukhaM nyaruNadashru purA sa yayOrdRshOH
atha tayOH pramadOtthitamapyadaH pratinirudhya giraM gururabravIt || 3-10 ||

ayi sutedamudAhara tattvatO nanu samAgatavAnasi sAmpratam
svajanatArahitasya tu kO.atra te sahacarO.arbhaka dIrghatame pathi || 3-11 ||

janakavAcamimAmavadhArayaNkalamudAharadamburuhekSaNaH
svapadamAvrajatO vrajatO.apyatO nanu sakhA mama kAnanagO vibhuH || 3-12 ||

taditarAyatanAttu yadAgamaM kRtanatiH khalu tatra hariH sakhA
ahamihApi mahendradigAlayaM praNatavAnuta yAvadadhIshvaram || 3-13 ||

api tatO.ahamupetya sahAmunA bhagavate.atra sate praNatiM vyadhAm
iti nigadya vibhAti shishuH sma vismitasabhAjanacIrNasabhAjanaH || 3-14 ||

virahitasvajanaM caraNapriyaM vividhabhUtabhaya~Nkaravartmani
ayi kRpAlaya pAlaya bAlakaM laghushubhasya mametyanamad dvijaH || 3-15 ||

tamupagRhya sutaM sutapOnidhirgRhamasau gRhiNIsahitO yayau
udayatIti hi bAladivAkare smitamabhUt sujanAnanavArijam || 3-16 ||

varavimAnagirAvapi caNDikA shishumahO jananI tamalAlayat
aparathA parituSTamanAH kathaM ciramihaiSa vasedvisahAyakaH || 3-17 ||

sakalashabdamayI ca sarasvatI satatamAnamati svayameva yam
dvijavarO.atha kadAcana mAtRkAH kila sutaM paricAyayati sma tam || 3-18 ||

lipikulaM nanu tAta gate dine likhitameva punarlikhitaM kutaH
iti nijapratibhAguNabhAvitaM haripadasya vacastamanandayat || 3-19 ||

shishurasau pratibhAmbudhirityalaM janamanOvacanagrahapID anA
na bhavatAditi taM vijanasthale svatanayaM samashikSayadeSakaH || 3-20 ||

mahavatA svajanena samIritasvajananIsahitena kadAcana
ruciravAcanayA.arcitavAkshriyA prati yaye prabhuNA ghRtavalyapi || 3-21 ||

pariSadA nitarAM parivAritaH shivapadaH kila dhautapaTOdbhavaH
iha kathAM kathayaNdadRshe tataH pRthudhiyA pRthukAkRtinA.amunA || 3-22 ||

idamuvAca vicAravicakSaNaH shucivacaH shanakaiH sa janAntare
aparathA kathitaM kathaka tvayA nanu matAt mahatAmiti sasmitam || 3-23 ||

agaNayanna shivaM janatA tadA savacane vasudevasutAhvaye
mukharamicchati kO mRgadhUrtakaM prakRtahu~NkRtasiM hashishau sati || 3-24 ||

atha kathAM kathayeti tadA jane gaditavatyucitArthamudAharat
sa samalAlyata vismayibhirnarairapi surairvijayA~NkurapUjakaiH || 3-25 ||

sa jananIsahitO janakaM gRhe pragatavAM stamudantamavedayat
nigada tAta shivaH kathakaH sa kiM vitathagIrathavA.ahamitIrayaN || 3-26 ||

nanu sutAvitathaM kathitaM tvayetyamumudIrya savismayamasmarat
prakRtitaH kRtitA khalu me shishOrmadadhinAthadayOdayajetyasau || 3-27 ||

kathayatAM prathame kathayatyalaM svajanake janasa~NghavRte kathAm
sakalalOkamanOnayanOtsavashcaturadhIH sa kadAcidavAcayat || 3-28 ||

vividhashAkhipadArthanivedane likucanAmni tadA.anuditArthake
kimiti tAta tadarthamavarNayaNkathayasIti shanairayamabravIt || 3-29 ||

avadatIti pitaryapi cOdite pratibubhutsuSu tatra janeSvapi
ayamudIrya tadarthamavAptavANpariSadO hyasamAnasumAnanAm || 3-30 ||

bahuvidhaishcaritairiti cArubhiH sakalalOkakutUhalakAriNam
dvijavareNa vayasyucite sthitaM tamupanetumanena dadhe manaH || 3-31 ||

samucitagrahayOgaguNAnvitaM samavadhArya muhUrtamadUSaNam
praNayabandhurabAndhavavAnasau dvijakulAkulamutsavamAtanOt || 3-32 ||

vividhavedatayA vijihIrSavO vadanara~Ngapade.asya cirAya yAH
suravarapramadA api sapriyA abhinanandurahO viyatO maham || 3-33 ||

vihitasAdhanasAdhitasatkriyOjjvalanamujjvaladhIrjvalayannayam
upaninAya sutaM samala~NkRtaM kushalinaM kushalIkRtashIrSakam || 3-34 ||

paricarAgnigurU caritavrataH sucaraNaH paTha sAdhu sadAgamAn
iti gurOstrijagadgurushikSaNe sphuTamahAsi suraiH kRtasAkSibhiH || 3-35 ||

jitakumAraguNaM sukumArakaM nijakumAramavekSya nirantaram
samucitAcaraNe caturaM svataH kSitisurO mudamAyata shikSayan || 3-36 ||

sa paTakhaNDamaki~ncanavat kvacit svavibhavAnucitaM caraNAdikam
bhuvanabharturahO svanigUhanaM surasabhAsu kutUhalamAtanOt || 3-37 ||

aviralairgaralOSmabhirAkulIkRtasamastajanO vicacAra yaH
kvacidamuM nijaghAM surashAntimAnupasasarpa sa sarpamayO.asuraH || 3-38 ||

tvaritamudyatavistRtamastakaH pratidadaM sha yadainamavikSatam
prabhupadAruNacArutarA~NgulIvihRtipiSTatanuH pratatAma saH || 3-39 ||

garuDatuNDamiva pratipannavANdvijakumArapadaM sa mamAra ca
samucitaM caritaM mahatAmidaM sumanasO manaseSTamapUjayan || 3-40 ||

girishagurvamarendramukhaishca yaccaraNareNuradhAri surAdhipaiH
kSitisurA~NghryabhivandanapUrvakaM sa vidadhe.adhyayanaM chalamAnuSaH || 3-41 ||

karatale khalu kandukavat sadA sakalayA kalayA saha vidyayA
aridhareNa samaM sphuritaM gurOrmanasi tasya viDambayatO janAn || 3-42 ||

anadhikairadhikaishca vayasyathO bahubhiradhyayanOparamAntare
anikaTe vaTubhiH paTubhirgurOH sa vijahAra sukhI sakhibhiH samam || 3-43 ||

padamudIrya javena yiyAsitaM drutasakheSvabhavat sa puraHsaraH
ayamayatnatayeti na vismayO nanu manOjavajit pavanO hyasau || 3-44 ||

plavanatejasi hanta na kevalaM vijitavANsa tadA sakalANjanAn
prabhunideshakarO hanumattanau nanu jigAya sa vAlisutAdikAN || 3-45 ||

jalavihAraparAjayibhiH spRdhA sakhibhirIritavAriparishritam
vadanamAkulalOcanamAdadhe smitamamuSya hi ka~ncana vibhramam || 3-46 ||

sa shanakairbalinO yugapadgatAnpravihRteSu sakhINnirapAtayat
ashanakairyugapat prakRtAhavAnsahasitO dvijasUnurayatnavAn || 3-47 ||

grahaNanigrahaNe grahaNe dRDhe gurubharOddharaNAdividhau paTau
iha vibhAvupacAradhiyA nRNAmRtamayaM nanu bhIma itIritam || 3-48 ||

viharatIti paThatyapi na sphuTaM svagRhagAmini cAdrutamAyati
paritutOSa na tatra jagadgurau sa kila pUgavanAnvayajO dvijaH || 3-49 ||

atha kadAcana sO.adhyayanAntare tamavadat kupitO.anyamanasvinam
paThasi nO shaTha te sakhibhiH samaM kimiti nityamudAsitadhIriti || 3-50 ||

guNanikA caraNAdikagOcarA na mama hRddayitetyudite.amunA
vada vishAradavAda yathepsitaM tvamuparItyavadaddharaNIsuraH

|| 3-51 ||

sakalalakSaNashikSaNamUlabhUH shrutisamAmananaM skhalanOjjhitam
na khalu kevalamasya gurOrvyadhAt sumanasAmapi tatra kutUhalam || 3-52 ||

priyavayasyashirOguruvedanAmashamayat sahajAmapi duHsahAm
sa vipine vijane mukhavAyunA shravaNagOcaritena kadAcana || 3-53 ||

adhigatOpaniSacca sakRcchrutA prakaTabhAgavatIti na vismayaH
adhigatA nanu jAtvapi na shrutAH pratibhayA shrutayaH shatashO.amunA

|| 3-54 ||

sAkSAdathOpaniSadO vibhuraittareyyAH pAThacchalena vijane.artharasAnbruvANaH
adhyApakAya vitatAra vimOkSabIjaM gOvindabhaktimucitAM gurudakSiNAM saH || 3-55 ||

ayi svAmiNduSTAndamaya damaya vyaktamacirAt
guNAngUDhAnviSNOH kathaya kathaya svAnpramadayan
tadA.anandaM tanvanniti sumanasAM sO.anusaratA
manujnAmAdatta tribhuvanagururbrAhmaNagurOH || 3-56 ||

iti shrImatkavikulatilaka trivikramapaNDitAcAryasuta
nArAyaNapaNDitAcAryaviracite shrImatsumadhvavijaye
mahAkAvye AnandA~Nke tRtIyaH sargaH

caturthaH sargaH

athaiSa sallOkadayAsudhArdrayA sadAgamastena nirAsakAmayA
ramAvarAvAsabhuvA vishAradO vishAlayA.acintayadAtmanO dhiyA || 4-1 ||

ananyasa~NgAd guNasa~NgitA harerjanasya mAnaM tu vishiSTaceSTitam
asa~NgamasmAt prakaTIkarOmyahaM nijaM bhajaNpAramahaM syamAshramam || 4-2 ||

mama prabhOrnAparathA hi shObhate dviSatsu viSNuM yadadaNDadhAraNam
harisvasA nanvacirAdasadbhide bhavedatO nAsmi ca daNDadhArakaH || 4-3 ||

vicintayannitthamanantacintakaH samastasanyAsanibaddhanishcayaH
asAvanujnArthamathAnamaddhariM samastasaM vyApinamAtmadAyagam || 4-4 ||

nije jane kiM namasIti pRcchati bruvaNsvavastupraNatiM vyadhAmiti
gurOH kilAnveSaNavAnjagadgurustadA jagAmAkhilalOkashikSakaH || 4-5 ||

yatiryatAtmA bhuvi kashcanAbhavadvibhUSaNO bhUriviraktibhUSaNaH
na nAmamAtrAcchucimarthatO.api yaM janO.acyutaprekSamudAharat sphuTam || 4-6 ||

puraiSa kRSNAkarasiddhashuddhimadvarAnnabhuktyA kila pANDavAlaye
vishOdhitAtmA madhukRtpravRttimAM shcacAra kAM shcit parivatsarAnmudA || 4-7 ||

abhUtkushAstrAbhyasanaM na pAtakaM kramAgatAdvipratisAratO yateH
yathA kushastrAdhyasanaM muradviSaH padAmbuje vyAdhavarasya garhitam || 4-8 ||

vinItamAmnAyashirOvishAradaM sadaiva tattvaM prabubhutsumAdarAt
gururviditvOpagatAM nijAM mRtiM kadAcidUce tamupahvare giram || 4-9 ||

ahaM svayaM brahma na ki~ncidasti matparaM vijRmbheta yadA sphuTaM citiH
itIha mAyAsamayOpapAditaM niranvayaM suvrata mA sma vishvasIH || 4-10 ||

yadetadAtmaikyamupAsticOditaM na me gurOrapyaparOkSatAM gatam
purAtanAnAmapi saumya kutracit tatO mukundaM bhaja saMvide mudA || 4-11 ||

itIdamAdishya vacO vacasvini svake gurau lOkamathAnyamIyuSi
asevatAlOcya muhurgurOrgiraM sa rUpyapIThAlayamindirAvaram || 4-12 ||

subhaktinA tena sa bhaktavatsalO niSevitastatra paraM bubhutsunA
bhaviSyataH shiSyavarAddhi viddhi mAmiti praviSTaH puruSaM tamabhyadhAt || 4-13 ||

pratIkSamANaM tamanugrahaM mudA niSevamANaM punarambujekSaNam
satAM guruH kAraNamAnuSAkRtiryatiM prashAntaM tamupAsasAda saH || 4-14 ||

sutaM yatIndrAnucaraM virAgiNaM nishamya saM nyAsanibaddhamAnasam
suvatsalau rUpyatalAlayasthitaM viyOgatAntau pitarau samIyatuH || 4-15 ||

varAshramaste jaratOranAthayOrna jIvatOH syAdayi nandanAvayOH
sayAcanaM vAkyamudIrya tAvidaM parItya putrAya natiM vitenatuH || 4-16 ||

natirna shushrUSujanAya shasyate nataM bhavadbhyAM sphuTamatra sAmpratam
ahO vidhAtrA svayameva dApitA tadabhyanujneti jagAda sa prabhuH || 4-17 ||

anuttarajnaH sa tamarthayan punaH yatIndramAnamya gataH priyAyutaH
gRhe vasan kalpasamAn kSaNAnnayan sutAnanendOranishaM tatO.asmarat || 4-18 ||

sa cintayaNputramanOrathaM shucA punashca tIrtvOpagatO mahAnadIm
vratIshvarAnuvratamAtmanandanaM tamaikSata grAmavare maThAntare || 4-19 ||

sa~njAtakOpAkulitO dharAsurO mahAtmanAM la~NghanabhIrurapyalam
sutasya kaupInadhRtau hi sAhasapratishravO me dRDha ityabhASata || 4-20 ||

kSaNena kaupInadharO nijaM paTaM vidArya he tAta kuruSva sAhasam
itImamuktvA vibhurabravIt punaH shubhAntarAyaM na bhavAM shcarediti || 4-21 ||

na putra pitrOravanaM vinA shubhaM vadanti santO nanu tau sutau mRtau
nivartamAne na hi pAlakO.asti nau tvayIti vaktAramamuM sutO.abravIt || 4-22 ||

yadA viraktaH puruSaH prajAyate tadaiva sanyAsavidhiH shrutau shrutaH
na sa~NgahInO.api parivrajAmi vAmahaM tu shushrUSumakalpayanniti || 4-23 ||

bahushrutatvAdyadi tatsahe balAnna sA savitrI virahaM saheta te
iti dvijenAbhihite.anamat sa taM bhavAnanujnAM pradadAtviti bruvan || 4-24 ||

vicintya vidvAn sa niruttarIkRtastathA.astu mAtA.anuvadedyadIti tam
udIrya kRcchrAdupagamya mandiraM priyAsakAshe tamudantamabravIt || 4-25 ||

nishAcarAreriva lakSmaNaH purA vRkOdarasyeva surendranandanaH
gadO.atha shaureriva karmakRt priyaH subhaktimAnvishvavidO.anujO.abhavat || 4-26 ||

kadAcidApyAlayabuddhirAlayaM nivedayaNpAlakamenametayOH
dRDhasvasaM nyAsaniSedhanishcayAM dhavAnumatyedamuvAca mAtaram || 4-27 ||

varAshramAptiM mama saM vadasva mAM kadAcidapyamba yadIcchasIkSitum
yadanyathA deshamimaM parityajaNna jAtu dRSTerviSayO bhavAmi vaH || 4-28 ||

iti bruvANe tanaye kadAcidapyadarshanaM tasya mRternidarshanam
vicintya paryAkulitA cikIrSitaM sutasya kRcchrAnnyaruNanna sA shubhA || 4-29 ||

athOpagamyaiSa guruM jagadguruH prasAdya taM devavaraprasAditaH
sadA samastAshramabhAk sureshvarO visheSataH khalvabhajadvarAshramam || 4-30 ||

kriyAkalApaM sakalaM sa kAlavidvidhAnamArgeNa vidhAya kevalam
sadA prasannasya hareH prasattaye muhuH samastanyasanaM samabhyadhAt || 4-31 ||

anantamAtrAntamudAharanti yaM trimAtrapUrvaM praNavOccayaM budhAH
tadA.abhavadbhAvicaturmukhAkRtirjapAdhikArI yatirasya sUcitaH || 4-32 ||

guNAnurUpOnnatipUrNabOdha ityamuSya nAma dvijavRndavanditaH
udAharad bhUriyashA hi kevalaM na mantravarNaH sa ca mantravarNakaH || 4-33 ||

nira~NgarAgaM mukharAgavarjitaM vibhUSaNaM viSTapabhUSaNAyitam
amuM dhRtASADhamavekSya menire svabhAvashObhA.anupameti jantavaH || 4-34 ||

bhuja~NgabhUteshaviha~NgapAdikaiH pravanditaH sAvasarapratIkSaNaiH
nanAma sO.ayaM gurupUrvakAn yatIn ahO mahIyO mahatAM viDambanam || 4-35 ||

varAshramAcAravisheSashikSaNaM vidhitsurasyAcaritaM nishAmayan
visheSashikSAM svayamApya dhIradhIH yatIshvarO vismayamAyatAntaram || 4-36 ||

sa raupyapIThAlayavAsine yadA nanAma nAthAya mahAmatirmudA
tadA.amunA.agrAhi narapraveshinA bhuje bhujenAshu bhuja~NgashAyinA || 4-37 ||

cirAt sutattvaM prabubhutsunA tvayA niSevaNaM me yadakAri tatphalam
amuM dadAmItyabhidhAya sO.amunA tadA praNIya pradade.acyutAtmane || 4-38 ||

anugrahaM taM pratigRhya sAdaraM mudA.atmanA.aptAM kRtakRtyatAM smaran
abhUdasa~NgO.api sa tatsusa~NgavAnasa~NgabhUSA nanu sAdhusa~NgitA || 4-39 ||

yiyAsati svastaTinIM muhurmuhurnamatyanujnArthini bhUricetasi
tamasmarat svAminameva dUnadhIrgururbhaviSyadvirahAgnisha~NkayA || 4-40 ||

itastRtIye divase dyunimnagA tvadarthamAsmAkataT AkamAvrajet
atO na yAyA iti taM tadA.avadat pravishya ka~ncit karuNAkarO hariH || 4-41 ||

tadAjnayOpAgatajAhnavIjale janO.atra sasnau saha pUrNabuddhinA
tataH paraM dvAdashavatsarAntare sadA.avrajet sA tadanugrahA~NkinI || 4-42 ||

gate dinAnAM dashake samAsake varAshramaM prApya sapatralambanam
jigAya jaitrAn bahutarkakarkashAn sa vAsudevAhvayapaNDitAdikAn || 4-43 ||

gurOH svashiSyaM caturaM cikIrSataH pracOdanAcchrOtumihOpacakrame
atheSTasiddhishchalajAtivAridhirnirAdareNApi mahAtmanA.amunA || 4-44 ||

tadAdyapadyasthamavadyamaNDalaM yadA.avadat SODashakadvayAtmakam
uparyapAstaM taditi bruvatyasau gurau tamUce praNigadyatAmiti || 4-45 ||

bhavatpravaktRtvasamarthatA na me sakOpamitthaM bruvati vratIshvare
apIha mAyAsamaye paTau nRNAM babhUva taddUSaNasaM shayA~NkuraH || 4-46 ||

budhO.abhidhAnaM shravaNaM budhetarO dhruvaM vidadhyAdvimumukSurAtmanaH
yatirvisheSAditi lOkacOdanAt pravakti mAyAsamayaM sma pUrNadhIH || 4-47 ||

akhaNDitOpanyasanaM visaM shayaM sasampradAyaM pravacO dRDhOttaram
samAgama~nchrOtumamuSya sAgrahA janAH shrutADhyAshcaturA bubhUSavaH || 4-48 ||

gurOrupAnte shravaNe ratairdvijaiH sapa~ncaSairbhAgavate kadAcana
bahuprakAre likhite tu vAcite prakAramekaM prabhurabhyadhAd dRDham || 4-49 ||

paraprakAreSvapi sambhavatsu te vinirNayO.asmiNkathamityudIrite
mukundabOdhena mahAhRdabravIt prakAramekaM bhagavatkRtaM sphuTam || 4-50 ||

nigadyatAM gadyamihaiva pa~ncame jagadgurOrvettha kRtisthitiM yadi
iti bruvANe yatisattame svayaM taduktamArgeNa jagAda bhUrihRt || 4-51 ||

asheSashiSyaishca tadAjnayA tadA parIkSaNAyaikSi samastapustakam
sa tatra hantaikatamesthitaM tyajaNna tAvadadhyAyanikAyamabhyadhAt || 4-52 ||

atra janmani na yatpaThitaM te jaitra bhAti kathamityamunOkte
pUrvajanmasu hi veda puredaM sarvamityamitabuddhiruvAca || 4-53 ||

iti bahuvidhavishvAshcaryacittapravRtteH
jagati vitatimAyannUtanA.apyasya kIrtiH
kSapitatatatamaskA bhAskarIva prabhA.alam
sujanakumudavRndAnandadA candrikeva || 4-54 ||

iti shrImatkavikulatilaka trivikramapaNDitAcAryasuta
nArAyaNapaNDitAcAryaviracite shrImatsumadhvavijaye
mahAkAvye AnandA~Nke caturthaH sargaH

pa~ncamaH sargaH

vedAntavidyAnijarAjyapAlane sa~NkalpyamAnO guruNA garIyasi
adabhracetA abhiSicyate purA sa vAribhirvArijapUritairatha || 5-1 ||

AnandarUpasya parasya pAtradhIrAnandasandAyisushAstrakRt sa yat
AnandatIrtheti padaM gurUditaM babhUva tasyAtyanurUparUpakam || 5-2 ||

kadAcidatrOpayayau yatiH sakhA gOvindabuddherbahushiSyasaM vRtaH
amuSya shiSyA anumAnashikSitAstadA.ajigISaNgurubuddhimuddhatAH || 5-3 ||

bhidA susAdhyetyanumAnamatra taiH prAyujyatAshu pratipakSabhISaNam
akhaNDayadvyaktamakhaNDadhIridaM sa pakSadakSaH phaNinaM virADiva || 5-4 ||

athApi mithyA vimataM matatvatO vivAdanirmuktavadityavAdi taiH
anena satyaM vimataM matattvatO yathA ghaTAdItyanumA nyagadyata || 5-5 ||

hetOrativyAptiravAdi tairyadA sakautukaistUrNamasAvavismayaH
na shuktirUpyAdi mataM yadanyathAmataM tadityAdi vadaNjigAya tAn || 5-6 ||

tattve.apyatattve vimate.anumAM vadaNtadapratiSThAM pratipAdukaH svayam
vijitya vishvAn viduSaH sabhAsvasau jagAma nAmnA.apyanumAnatIrthatAm || 5-7 ||

samastavAdIndragajaprabha~NgadashcarannavanyAM pratipakSakA~NkSayA
