vidveSTA shrutiguNasAdhakaM shrutInAm
vAcAlO vacanamuvAca vAgmivaryam || 16-2 ||

unmattapralapitavanna taddhi mAnam
yadvAkyaM vyabhicarati kvacitphale.atra
dRSTAntO bhavati tadapramANatAyAm
sarveSAM shrutivacasAM ca sarvatheti || 16-3 ||

vedOktaM phalamalamApyate.adhikArAdityuktO.atanumanasA.abhyadhatta dhUrtaH
yOgyatve sati na hi dRshyate.adhikArI
nAtaH syAt sa kharaviSANavat sadeti || 16-4 ||

AkSepaM tamasahamAna uccamAnaH
sadyO.asau nijakarapallavadvayena
AdAya vyatanuta bIjamOSadhInAm
sUktenA~NkuradalapuSpabIjasRSTim || 16-5 ||

vyAkhyAtA nishi sa kadAcana pradIpe
saM shAnte punarapi vAcayAmbabhUva
shiSyAnsvAnpurukaruNAmbudhirnijA~Nghrera~NguSThasphuTanakharAntarOciSaiva || 16-6 ||

tIrthArthaM pRthutaravaprapAtivArAm
dhArANAM raya sahana kSamAM mahekSaH
AnItAM dashashatapumbhiratyashaktyA
prekSyOce vipulashilAM kvacitsa muktAm || 16-7 ||

lOkAnAmupakRtaye kutaH shileyam
ninye nO iti janatA jagAda tatra
netArO yativaraM mAnavA nahImAm
bhImashcediha yatate nayennaveti || 16-8 ||

ninye tAM girimiva vAnarIkRtAtmA
lIlAvatkarakamalena sO.amalena
tatrApi nyadhita tayA.asya sUcyate.alam
tattu~NgAM nanu nikaSA.adhunA.api karma || 16-9 ||

sa~NghAtairadhikathanairala~NkRtAdhvA
shiSyANAM yatamanasAmutetareSAm
yatrAmAvasati tithAvinena candrastatrAsau sakalamatiH sasAra sindhum || 16-10 ||

ArdrA~NgAH sapadi nimajjanAtsarasyAm
kaNvasya dvijaRSabhasya vallabhAyAm
tatrAyankharakiraNOparAgahetOrgrAmINA
api sakalAH sabAlavRddhAH || 16-11 ||

sarvajnaM saparijanaM samIkSamANAH
phullAkSAH smitavadanAH shubhAH nananduH
daurmukhyaM dadhata utApare ninindurnAshcarya dvayamapi tatsvabhAvatantram || 16-12 ||

mAmainaM bhuvanaguruM vinindatettham
nirbhartsyAbhyapatadivOttara~NgahastaH
sa~NkSObhI ghanaghanaghOSaghOraveSaH
saM rambhI khaladamanAya sindhurAjaH || 16-13 ||

saM mOdAttaralatarO drutAbhigAmI
gambhIra svana nutimAn suphenahAsaH
vIcya~NgaiH adhikataraiH iha adhivelam
madhvAya praNatimiva vyadhAt samudraH || 16-14 ||

gOlIlAsvatishayinAvagAdhabhAvAt
nOlla~Nghyau vividhaguNaprakAsharatnau
madhvAbdhI paramamateH priyaM janAnAm
lAvaNyaM na tu jaladherayaM visheSaH || 16-15 ||

ambhOdheH tvarita tarOrmi pANimRSTe
svacche.asau vikaTataTAsane niSaNNaH
vyAcakhyAvaticiramaitareyashAkhAsUktAni prabhuratisundaraprakAram || 16-16 ||

gAmbhIryAtsvanamadharIkarOti sindhOH
shrAvyatvaM vahati tathApyahO svanO.asya
pUrNenduprabhavadanaH ka eSa dhanyO
matvetthaM janajaladhistamAshu paryait || 16-17 ||

vedAnAM samucitabhAvavAdadakSam
ye vedadviSamimamUcire maherSyAH
dhig dhiktAniti janatA jagAda gADham
svAshcaryAtkila kalitA~njalirnamantI || 16-18 ||

sanmAnaM vipulahRde vidhAya bhaktyA
bibhrANAshcaraNarajO.asya devasevyam
tatsnnAnAdadhikashucau nadAdhirAje
sasnnuste dvijanikarAH prashastakAle || 16-19 ||

kallOlaiH karinikarairivAnivAryaiH
ullOlairjananikarAnnipAtayadbhiH
AkrAntAH prabalataraishca lOThyamAnA
hAsyatvamprayayurudanvatIha naike || 16-20 ||

majjantaM pRthulaharInigUD hamUrtim
sampUrNapramatimasajjanO jahAsa
yO lOkatrayavijayI guruH prasiddhaH
sO.ayaM hA patati laghUrmilIlayeti || 16-21 ||

nIcAnAmavacavacAM syajIgaNannO
dabhrANAM kSubhitakarANyadabhrasa~NkhyaH
krOSTUnAM shvakalakalapradaM virAvam
pa~ncAsyO na hi gaNayedudAravIryaH || 16-22 ||

janmasthityavasitidAyinaM kaTAkSam
lOkAnAmaghaTayadambudhau bRhaddhIH
AkrAntO.adhikaguruNA sa tena tAvan
mu~ncansa~ncalanamabhUttaT AkadeshyaH || 16-23 ||

ityAdyairapi caritairananyasAdhyaiH
na stheSThAM bahumatimApa durjanO.asmin
vidveSaM vyadhita punarnirastabhAgye
tasmindurmanasi tadeva shObhanaM syAt || 16-24 ||

samprAptaM saha sahajena gaNDavATam
svOjassamprakaT ana Adishadvisha~Nkam
shushrUSAmayamucitO vidhAtumISallOkAnAmiti vacasA parIkSakANAm || 16-25 ||

shrIkanteshvarasadane.anayatkilaikO
yastriM shannaravaranItaketuyaSTim
AhatyAgurugadayaiva nArikelAdyO
lebhe taralatarAtphalAni kAmam || 16-26 ||

etAdRgbalavibhavaH sa tasya kaNTham
tajjyeSThO.apyabhita ubhau samaM gRhItvA
niSpeSTuM paramamavApatuH prayatnam
sa~NgharSAtkramaparivardhamAnataikSNyam || 16-27 ||

AsvinnAvalasatarau gurOrniyOgAcchatrAgnyAnilamahitau ca tAvubhAbhyAm
muktvA.ayaH kaThinataratvacaM shirOdhim
paryAyasphuTavacanAM nipetatuH kau || 16-28 ||

Ashvastau shucihRdimAvanUnamAnAvuddhartuM samagadada~NgulIM dharAsthAm
sa~NgRhya prasabharasAdatiprayatnau64
sAmarthyaM yayaturimau na kampane.asyAH || 16-29 ||

niryatnaM vaTumadhiruhya mandahAsI
sa prAyAdiha paritO nRsiM hageham
aishvaryairiti laghimAdikairupetO
madhvO.abhUttribhuvanacitraratnarAjaH || 16-30 ||

pa~ncAshannarapanarOpanItamAtrAm
yO vArkSIM gRhamadhirOhiNIM ninAya
sa vyAkhyAsvaradamanAya pUrvavATO
nirdeshAdvyadhita gurOrgalaprapeSam || 16-31 ||

svinne.asminnapi yatamAna AgrahOgre
prAcyAttatpravacananisvanO.atireje
uddhartuM vipulahRda~NguliM ca nAlam
sO.abhUdityajani kutUhalaM janAnAm || 16-32 ||

paryaikSi prabhuritaraiH shivAgnipUrvaiH
nOpaikSi prabalataraistathA prayatnaiH
nAvaikSi kvacidapi shaktyapUrtirasmin
utpraikSi svayamapi bhIma ityavashyam || 16-33 ||

lekhinyA muhurapinahya kRSyamANam 
nApyekaM tanuruhamasya tUdapATi
nAsAgre mRduni kRtaishca muSTighAtaiH
nAsyendOratibalibhiH prasannatA.asi || 16-34 ||

pa~ncAsyaH shvabhiriva vai vihIna sAraiH ambhOdhir nadasaritAM jalairivAlpaiH
khadyOtairiva taraNirviDambayaNnRn
pratyarthisvasamanarairvyavAharatsaH || 16-35 ||

pArantIsurasadanaM vishAlasaM vit
samprAptaH khalu sucirAnnivedyahInam
grAmyAgryakSitipatibhirdinArdhamAtrAt
tadbhUtIrvyadhita sabhUtabalyanalpAH || 16-36 ||

bhImatve saha sahajaiH pratiSThitaH prAk
pa~ncAtmA muraripura~ncitO yadatra
pA~ncAlyA balisalilaM samaM dadatyA
sO.asmArSIttamimamatha prapUjyapUjyaH || 16-37 ||

AyAsyankila saridantarAkhyadesham
grISme nirjalamiha shushruvAM staTAkam
tatkAle paramabhivarSayaNghanaugham
tatpUrtyai vyadhita kutUhalaM narANAm || 16-38 ||

durmantraiH khalapaTalaiH pracOdyamAnO
grAmeshO vR.salapatiH prahartumenam
samprAptastata uta yAntamIkSamANaH
prOdyantaM ravimiva vismitO nanAma || 16-39 ||

kSetrAgryaM tribhuvanavaidyanAthanAtham
prasthAya pracuratarAntaraH prabhAvI
shrIkRSNAmRtaparamArNavAbhidhAnAm
cakre sadvacanatatiM svabhaktabhUtyai || 16-40 ||

sagrAmaM paramapi yAta uccabhUtim
vidvAmsah kva kuharakUpadardurAbhAH
ityUce madamatimAninO.akhilajnam
manyasya kSapayitumeva tajjanasya || 16-41 ||

sarvajnO.apyayamadhikaM na yajnabha~NgIm
samvitte yatiriti baddhanishcayO.asau
AbhAntaM pariSadi matsarAdapRcchat
karmArtha shruti gahanArtha khaNDabhAvam || 16-42 ||

chandObhyashcyutarasasa~NgrahapravINAn
SaSThe.ahni prativihitAnprajAdhipena
nArAshaM syacaramacArumantrabhedAnUce.asau tamabhidadhadvisaM shayAM shaH || 16-43 ||

pANDityaM paramamavekSya tasya tAdRk
sa~NgharSakSubhitamanA67 vipakSasa~NghaH
nArthaH syAdayamiti varNayannatha tvam
taM brUhItyurumatineritO.adravad drAk || 16-44 ||

sO.apRcchattamatha mahAhvayOpasargAm
yatrOktA manucaraNOpasRjyarUpAH
tasyArthaM vacanacayasya taM bruvANaH
sthairyArthaM sapadi sa lekhayAmbabhUva || 16-45 ||

sampUrNaM shashinamivOditaM kRshaH shvA
cukSObhAshubhanikarO nirIkSya madhvam
pratyarthI svayamiti dUratO.abhidhAvan68
kiM tena kSatamamRtAkarasya tasya || 16-46 ||

niHsvAnAM katipayabhuktiyuktabhaktam
bhaktAnAM vyadhita caturguNaM dayAluH
bhu~Nkte sma tridashanarOpabhOjyamannam
samprItyai sa dhanavatAM bRhatprabOdhaH || 16-47 ||

vRSTyAdeH sa niyamanAdi cakra etaccitraM kiM bhuvananiyAmake samIre
apyevaM bhuvanagurOH kRtAnuvAdaH
kRtyeSu pravara itIha varNayAmaH 
ityUce dharaNisureNa kevalaM nO || 16-48 ||

mAdhvIyaM vividhakathA kathAsu mAnyA
sa~NgharSAtkSubhitamanA dUravO.abhidhAvan
sAkSAdapyamaravarairudIryamANA
gandharvairdyusadasi tanmude jage.asau || 16-49 ||

tAM padyapraNigaditAM tu mUrcchayitvA 
tAnAnAmucitatayA.attapa~ncamAdyAH
gAndhAraM dyuviSayamujjvalaM sRjantO
grAmaM te prajagurakAkikamrakaNThAH || 16-50 ||

AnamraiH sumukuTamaulibhiH karAgraiH
AtAmraiH pratikalitaiH smitairmukhAbjaiH
AshrAvi sthiratarabhaktibhiH surendraiH
tadgItA dashadhiSaNAryavaryacaryA || 16-51 ||

gIrvANairvijayamahOtsavasya pUjAm
kurvANairaviralasaM vidastadAnIm
vismerairmuninikarOpadevayuktaiH
susmerairatha tamavekSituM prajagme || 16-52 ||

AdarshaM guNagaNadarshane murAreH
sacchAstraM racitamanena varNayantaH
pradyOteruDupadavIM prakAshayantaH
praikSanta pracuramanOvilAsamete || 16-53 ||

nAkIndrAH taM avani bhAgamAvasantam
sushlOkairapi bhuvanAni bhUSayantam
nemuH khAdupaniSadaM tadaitareyIm
vyAkhyAntaM vividha vishiSTa shisyamadhye || 16-54 ||

shrImantaM shashivadanaM kusheshayAkSam
gambhIrasvaramatidivyalakSaNADhyam
pashyantaH svagurumathArcayaNkRtArthA
vANyA taM hariratipUrNakAmamete || 16-55 ||

aharO durAgamatamaH svagOgaNairakarOrmukundaguNavRndadarshanam
ajayashcaturdashajaganti sadguNaiH
sharaNaM gurO karuNayA.api nO bhaveH || 16-56 ||

namaste prANesha praNatavibhavAyAvanimagAH
namaH svAmiNrAmapriyatama hanUmaNguruguNa
namastubhyaM bhIma prabalatama kRSNeSTa bhagavan
namaH shrImanmadhva pradisha sudRshaM nO jaya jaya || 16-57 ||

iti nigaditavantastatravRndArakendrA
guruvijayamahaM taM lAlayantO mahAntam
vavRSurakhiladRshyaM puSpavAraM sugandham
haridayitavariSThe shrImadAnandatIrthe || 16-58 ||

iti shrImatkavikulatilaka trivikramapaNDitAcAryasuta
nArAyaNapaNDitAcAryaviracite shrImatsumadhvavijaye
mahAkAvye AnandA~Nke SODashaH sargaH

samAptO.ayaM granthaH
